<div id="review_537127320" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/537127320" />
    <a title="Beth" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13485675-beth"><img alt="Beth" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/537127320?book_show_action=true">Feb 15, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Beth" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Beth" href="/user/show/13485675-beth">Beth</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140440751" href="/book/show/103390.The_Song_of_Roland">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13485675-beth?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13485675-beth?shelf=m-a-list">m-a-list</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13485675-beth?shelf=owned">owned</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13485675-beth?shelf=france">france</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13485675-beth?shelf=poetry">poetry</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13485675-beth?shelf=middle-ages">middle-ages</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer537127320" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17563088974520239849">Heroism. Blood and gore. Larger than life characters. Betrayal. Honor. Revenge. The blows of French axes against Saracen scimitars. All the elements of good epic poetry. <br/><br/>Dorothy Sayers’ translation is lyric and poetic, and capitalizes on the medieval feel of archaic language. I found her notes helpful, but also found it bit distracting when she slightly altered the characters names in order to make them fit better with the meter. The French translation that I read (by Léon Gautier) used much mor</span>
  <span id="freeText17563088974520239849" style="display:none">Heroism. Blood and gore. Larger than life characters. Betrayal. Honor. Revenge. The blows of French axes against Saracen scimitars. All the elements of good epic poetry. <br /><br />Dorothy Sayers’ translation is lyric and poetic, and capitalizes on the medieval feel of archaic language. I found her notes helpful, but also found it bit distracting when she slightly altered the characters names in order to make them fit better with the meter. The French translation that I read (by Léon Gautier) used much more straightforward language – not distractingly modern, but also much easier to follow than the King James style English of the Sayers translation. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="17563088974520239849" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


